sentences: Sakiko Matsui (松井咲子, Matsui Sakiko, born December 10, 1990 in Warabi, Saitama Prefecture) is a Japanese singer and pianist.
She was a member of AKB48.

Concurrently as a student specializing in piano at Tokyo College of Music, she has released a piano instrumental album Kokyū Suru Piano on October 3, 2012, which reached number 10 on Oricon's albums chart.
ja:Kokyū Suru Piano (2012) - Reached number 10 on Oricon.
